  <summary>10/5/1999--Introduced.
Electronic Commerce Crime Prevention and Protection Act - Prohibits any person from making or publishing a notice or advertisement, that will be transported in interstate or foreign commerce by computer, for producing, obtaining, or disposing of a firearm, ammunition, or explosive material.</summary>
